# Adaptation Core — kanon (L1–L3)

Kanon: [`shared/adaptation/adaptationTypes.ts`](../../shared/adaptation/adaptationTypes.ts) · [`shared/adaptation/adaptationSemanticTypes.ts`](../../shared/adaptation/adaptationSemanticTypes.ts)

## MUST

- **Core-silo only** — `adaptation_prefs`, `adaptation_ledger`, `adaptation_semantic_profile` byggs aldrig från Valv/Kunskap/Barnen
- **Deterministisk kod före LLM** för ton (`coachTone`), täthet (`uiDensity`) och signal-merge
- **Server-gated flags:** `adaptation_layer_v1`, `adaptation_semantic_v1` via `evolution_hub.unlockedFeatureFlags` (Admin SDK only)
- **L3a tone** = bank-transform only (`MABRA_COACH_BANK.text_sv` + `lens`) — U6 P1 parafras
- **Ledger audit** server-only via `onAdaptationPrefsWrite` (`source: system`)
- **Logout cleanup:** `resetAdaptationSignalThrottle()` + `useAdaptationStore.reset()` i `signOutUser`
- **Smoke:** `npm run smoke:adaptation` + `npm run smoke:adaptation-l3a` vid adaptation/MåBra-ton-ändringar

## MUST NOT

- Fjärde RAG-silo eller cross-RAG från adaptation till Valv/Kunskap/Barnen
- LLM skriver `adaptation_prefs` eller `adaptation_ledger`
- Client styr `coachTone` via callable input — server läser `adaptation_prefs/{uid}`
- User note / optionalNote i deterministic coach text
- Client dual-write till `adaptation_ledger` (server trigger är enda writer)

## Deploy-gate

YOLO-vakt GO + `npm run smoke:locked-ux` + `npm run smoke:adaptation` före deploy av adaptation/MåBra functions.
